<h1 class="call"><a name="histories"><%= title %></a></h1>

<p>
Whenever a device changes its properties a new history resource is created.
This happens in different ways, like executing a function or interacting with the
physical world.
</p>

<p>
This resource saves the changed device properties and can be used to extract usage
patterns to improve the way you live your house.
</p>

</article>

