<article>

  <h1 class="call"><a name="get-a-history">GET /histories/:id</a></h1>

  <p>
    Returns extended information for a given history identified from its ID
    (the device described in the history resource must be owned).
  </p>

  <h4>Resource URL</h4>
  <div class="preview">
  <pre><code class="no-highlight">GET http://api.lelylan.com/histories/:id</code></pre>
  </div>

